    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138410/extras/80c359f4986120389f5a3cb61d129b00.avif?t=1760370357\" width=600 height=180 /></span><br><br><strong>《芜菁山》是一款拥有独特操作方式的解谜平台游戏。操控双手抓住墙壁，攀登至山顶！</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138410/extras/1fb6e7669052729638811f0dfc83a3a8.poster.avif?t=1760370357\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138410/extras/1fb6e7669052729638811f0dfc83a3a8.webm?t=1760370357\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138410/extras/1fb6e7669052729638811f0dfc83a3a8.mp4?t=1760370357\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >核心特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 拿起手柄，开始抓取！</li></ul>使用双摇杆伸手并抓住最近的墙面。<br>攀登木桩，从旋转轮盘上弹射自己，抓住摇摆的绳索，并与自然元素对抗，向山顶前进。<br>善用惯性，你能攀上更高的高度！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138410/extras/4114cb741eea7a197493234132b1de13.poster.avif?t=1760370357\" width=600 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138410/extras/4114cb741eea7a197493234132b1de13.webm?t=1760370357\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138410/extras/4114cb741eea7a197493234132b1de13.mp4?t=1760370357\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 自定义！</li></ul>途中能拾取大量装饰品——调个色板换换风格，或者戴上炫酷的头饰！<br>没有道具，没有升级，只有你和这座山。<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 可重复游玩！</li></ul>在这段短小却精致的冒险中，有分支道路与多条登顶路线——你会遇到什么呢？<br>还能挑战计时赛！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138410/extras/feca0da89de8043d7f924e7a87f5fc1f.poster.avif?t=1760370357\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138410/extras/feca0da89de8043d7f924e7a87f5fc1f.webm?t=1760370357\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138410/extras/feca0da89de8043d7f924e7a87f5fc1f.mp4?t=1760370357\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
